  {
    "chunk_id": "mineru_jiaocaineedrop_jiaocai_needrop_en_2496_3",
    "text": "2.切割线定理：如下右图，PT为圆O的切线，PAB、PCD为割线，则PT2=PA·PB()； 3.割线定理：如下右图，PAB、PCD为圆O的割线，则PA·PB=PC·PD.",
